<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 12:13:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>因人质营救而推迟后，以色列甘茨预计将宣布退出内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</link><description>原定于周六举行的新闻发布会——本尼·甘茨部长为退出政府设定的最后期限，以免哈马斯后加沙政府的计划获得批准——在四名以色列人质从加沙获救的消息传出后被推迟到周日</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 11:56:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/after-delay-due-to-hostage-rescue-gantz-expected-to-announce-exit-from-netanyahu-govt/0000018f-fca1-d93d-abbf-feb3ed5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列残奥会网球选手在罗兰·加洛斯赢得首个大满贯冠军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</link><description>盖伊·萨森（Guy Sasson）在四人轮椅轮椅组单打比赛中排名世界第三，击败了排名第二的萨姆·施罗德（Sam Schröder）。萨森表示，他的胜利属于以色列，并将其献给在周六的救援任务中被释放的四名人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 10:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-paralympic-tennis-player-wins-first-grand-slam-title-in-roland-garros/0000018f-fc4b-d5ad-ad8f-fc4bd55e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列频道因对获救人质的出现发表不敏感言论而解雇主播</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</link><description>“看她的眉毛，比我的好看！”阿拉伯以色列电视节目主持人拉马·塔图尔 (Lama Tatour) 在 Instagram 上发帖，提到了诺亚·阿格马尼 (Noa Argmani) 的外貌，她在被哈马斯囚禁九个月后在人质营救行动中被释放</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:49:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/israeli-channel-fires-anchor-after-insensitive-comments-about-rescued-hostages-appearance/0000018f-fc17-d93d-abbf-fe377a200000</guid></item><item><title>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出卡塔尔并不会让辛瓦尔同意加沙停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</link><description>将哈马斯领导人驱逐出他们在卡塔尔的舒适避难所可能是一种严厉的个人惩罚，但这不太可能对加沙的辛瓦尔产生影响。如果哈尼亚有真正的影响力，那就是替代政府，而不是哈尼亚在卡塔尔享有的“保障性住房”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 09:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/expelling-hamas-leaders-from-qatar-wont-make-sinwar-agree-to-a-gaza-cease-fire-deal/0000018f-fc03-df2e-a5df-fe7735240000</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚因加沙战争暂停向以色列出口煤炭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/colombia-to-suspend-coal-exports-to-israel-over-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fbea-d93d-abbf-fbfb582b0000</link><description>尽管依赖以色列武器，哥伦比亚总统仍将煤炭出口与结束以色列-加沙战争联系起来，同时呼吁其他国家效仿</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 08:26:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/colombia-to-suspend-coal-exports-to-israel-over-war-in-gaza/0000018f-fbea-d93d-abbf-fbfb582b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说不幸的是，内塔尼亚胡只有在有好消息时才会出现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</link><description>当以色列军队大胆营救人质时，内塔尼亚胡出现在每张照片中，并在每台电视上发表讲话。但正如一名死去人质的父亲雄辩而悲惨地说的那样，“当结局不好时，首相就不会出现。”他也不打电话”</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/unfortunately-for-israelis-netanyahu-only-shows-up-when-theres-good-news/0000018f-f96c-d084-abef-ff6d2db20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称至少有 10 枚火箭弹从黎巴嫩发射到边境社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</link><description>以色列特种部队军官在救援行动中身亡 ■ 美国恢复通过人道主义码头向加沙运送援助物资 ■ 哈马斯报告加沙中部有 200 多人丧生 ■ 以色列高等法院命令国家解释为何不会取消负责关闭半岛电视台的法案■ 以色列国防军估计至少有 10 枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 02:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article-live/police-use-water-cannons-make-arrests-at-tel-aviv-protest-calling-for-hostage-deal/0000018f-fab3-d3fb-a1af-ffbb4ead0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙解救四名人质对厌倦战争的以色列人来说是一记强心针，但远未达到“全面胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</link><description>虽然这一成就肯定会鼓舞仍在加沙作战的以色列国防军士兵的斗志，但这并不预示着战争方式的战略改变 — — 并可能导致哈马斯在停火谈判中加强其要求</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/rescue-of-four-hostages-from-gaza-a-greatly-needed-shot-in-the-arm-for-war-weary-israelis/0000018f-f97b-df2e-a5df-ff7f10670000</guid></item><item><title>美国向以色列提供营救人质情报，但参与程度尚不清楚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</link><description>以色列和美国官员指出，美国参与了以色列在加沙的人质营救任务的情报收集，但声称显示援助卡车和作为行动一部分的美国建造的码头的图像招致了批评，因为人质交易的未来已成定局。在空中</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 21:08:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-provided-intelligence-to-israel-for-hostage-rescue-but-involvement-is-unclear/0000018f-f943-de5e-a5ef-fdc7ef1b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员不确定救援行动将如何影响与哈马斯的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</link><description>以色列和调解员正在等待哈马斯对乔·拜登提出的“以色列计划”的正式回应，消息人士称哈马斯的“同意”将对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡施加巨大压力</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 20:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/unclear-whether-rescue-will-aid-or-delay-deal-to-free-remaining-hostages/0000018f-f94b-dc3c-a9cf-f97fec3b0000</guid></item><item><title>获救的以色列人质诺亚·阿加玛尼与身患绝症的母亲团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</link><description>哈马斯上周发布的一段视频中可以听到诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 的声音，八个月后，周六，他与另外三名人质在以色列的一次行动中从加沙获救。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 19:08:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/rescued-israeli-hostage-noa-argamani-reunited-with-her-terminally-ill-mother/0000018f-f909-df2e-a5df-ff7d532c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人抗议，呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</link><description>周六晚上，以色列各地爆发了抗议活动，在场人士呼吁达成协议，归还剩余 120 名人质并提前举行选举。警方在海法驱散反战抗议者，并在特拉维夫逮捕了33名反战抗议者</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-protest-across-israel-call-for-govt-to-accept-hostage-deal/0000018f-f90b-dc3c-a9cf-f93f2bcf0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大胆救援行动证明：人质还活着，只有达成协议才能拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡周六赶到示巴医院与被释放的人质合影，但他尚未会见上周宣布死亡的人质家属。与此同时，总理的喉舌已经在利用救援行动来抹黑领导人的竞争对手</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-rescue-operation-proves-hostages-are-still-alive-only-a-deal-will-save-them/0000018f-f8de-d084-abef-fedfc8280000</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争和内塔尼亚胡的政策，以色列妇女权利降至新低</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/womens-rights-in-israel-at-a-new-low-due-to-gaza-war-and-netanyahus-policies/0000018f-ed6f-dd70-a7df-fd6f1f8c0000</link><description>根据以色列民主研究所的一份报告，由于 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击、随后发生的加沙战争以及国内家庭暴力，以色列的暴力侵害妇女行为将在 2024 年出现前所未有的激增，该报告还警告称，以色列将妇女排除在外。决策论坛中的女性</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 18:00:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/womens-rights-in-israel-at-a-new-low-due-to-gaza-war-and-netanyahus-policies/0000018f-ed6f-dd70-a7df-fd6f1f8c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称光天化日之下同时从加沙公寓救出人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-hostages-rescued-from-gaza-apartments-simultaneously-in-broad-daylight/0000018f-f8aa-d084-abef-feeb55250000</link><description>以色列军队表示，根据情报，这次任务的准备工作在几周前就开始了，他们按照恩德培行动等模式进行了训练。以色列军队遭到包括火箭弹在内的猛烈射击，一名军官受重伤，后来因伤重不治身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 17:54:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-hostages-rescued-from-gaza-apartments-simultaneously-in-broad-daylight/0000018f-f8aa-d084-abef-feeb55250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 246 天：以色列在加沙中部的行动中救出四名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-246-four-hostages-rescued-in-israeli-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f8b9-d7d0-af9f-fdfd6b950000</link><description>以色列在加沙中部的行动中四名人质被生还；一名特种部队军官被杀 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：210 名巴勒斯坦人在以色列国防军行动中丧生，400 多人受伤 ■ 以色列医院官员：获救人质状况良好且“精神状态良好” ■ 以下是 245 天后您需要了解的信息战争</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 16:58:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-246-four-hostages-rescued-in-israeli-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f8b9-d7d0-af9f-fdfd6b950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列特种部队军官在加沙解救人质行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-killed-in-gaza-operation-to-free-hostages/0000018f-f86d-d93d-abbf-fa7f77d30000</link><description>10月7日，总督察阿农·兹莫拉在以色列南部奋力击退恐怖分子，在成功解救四名人质后身亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:54:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-special-forces-officer-killed-in-gaza-operation-to-free-hostages/0000018f-f86d-d93d-abbf-fa7f77d30000</guid></item><item><title>八个月零一天后：四名人质与亲人团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-eight-months-and-one-day-four-israeli-hostages-reunited-with-their-loved-ones/0000018f-f859-d93d-abbf-fa7b39e70000</link><description>诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani)、阿尔莫格·梅厄·扬 (Almog Meir Jan)、安德烈·科兹洛夫 (Andrey Kozlov) 和什洛米·齐夫 (Shlomi Ziv) 在示巴医疗中心与亲人团聚</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-eight-months-and-one-day-four-israeli-hostages-reunited-with-their-loved-ones/0000018f-f859-d93d-abbf-fa7b39e70000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯称以色列在加沙中部解救人质行动中至少有210人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/hamas-says-at-least-210-killed-in-israeli-hostage-rescue-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f84c-d084-abef-fe4d4a760000</link><description>在解救四名人质的行动中，以色列国防军从空中、海上和陆地袭击了努塞拉特和代尔巴拉赫。哈马斯卫生部称，死亡人数预计还会上升，附近医院难以应对不断增加的伤亡人数</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 15:26:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/hamas-says-at-least-210-killed-in-israeli-hostage-rescue-operation-in-central-gaza/0000018f-f84c-d084-abef-fe4d4a760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列甘茨取消预期宣布退出内塔尼亚胡政府的新闻发布会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/gantz-cancels-expected-press-conference-announcing-departure-from-netanyahu-government/0000018f-f828-df2e-a5df-fe7dbe180000</link><description>在成功营救四名以色列人质后，甘茨推迟了宣布这一消息的时间，但预计将在未来几天内选择新的日期</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 14:21:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/gantz-cancels-expected-press-conference-announcing-departure-from-netanyahu-government/0000018f-f828-df2e-a5df-fe7dbe180000</guid></item></channel></rss>